{"tid":1471924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同總統先生傾過，佢話香港一定會救，但首先大家唔好割晒蓆先","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:23:53.000Z","uid":33307,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"12941feec46530a313e8b98cdf44e675f99a58ac","tid":1471924,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"如果唔係美軍黎到會好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5336ab4a2b33fc752178b3f5ebdec98f45e4bfb2","tid":1471924,"uid":192824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"幫我同總統先生講，美軍來我加入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b49cd6eb4aa6df886b500068bf52f906ea7996d","tid":1471924,"uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"總統先生已經留意到香港人揮動美國旗，示意需要人道援助<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJK2z8G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJK2z8G.png&h=5fd28099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c309689a9e2b75d60c36e429c9e676356db0bfd","tid":1471924,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b31581db5c8f7249cfe5d690742a56e599a363","tid":1471924,"uid":78143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtSr6ei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtSr6ei.jpg&h=a12ccc2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f30c6c781b0eee99d54daa6589910ba7b5af0371","tid":1471924,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"另外總統先生已經收到情報機構消息，老解已駐於香港外圍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhJCn07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhJCn07.jpg&h=73fa073c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e8a5320eeafce6f75c16951b83b133d576ccd4c","tid":1471924,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「重要！同我勁推」有高人教路如何找出popo前線鬼的痕跡<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢身份證簽發日期,因為popo係優先換證的。日期係由2018年12月27日至2019年3月30日。如係呢三個月,就九成九了。<br />\n如果隻鬼係打算長期混入去D團體度的,便例外。<br />\n如條友唔比身份證你睇,即係唔交心,更要小心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都是聽番來 不確定有冇用 希望幫到巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">有人話比證件人看很危險 其實只需大家互看簽發日期一欄 其他資料遮住都可</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我P牌開唔到新post今日 唔介意有巴絲copy開個專門post緊急宣傳比大家知道同研究</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f32234dddce520d10bb56fd369fc8038c56b6f76","tid":1471924,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以問下總統先生<br />\n矮到成個女仔咁可唔可以破例入美軍"},{"pid":"ea1e9f8fdecb54f8aa6ab6e418db11640c94c837","tid":1471924,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"另外總統先生已經非常關注香港執法機構既暴行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BQxcM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BQxcM8.jpg&h=9a0feda9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b7e668a3a133fc0e0f4c7a201663f5a9e80430b","tid":1471924,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5336ab4a2b33fc752178b3f5ebdec98f45e4bfb2","tid":1471924,"uid":192824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"幫我同總統先生講，美軍來我加入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"做軍妓都嫌你屎忽唔夠彈手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc6859a3b458cbba859d9330ec2b7c916c92654","tid":1471924,"uid":33307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"總統先生另外問我：點解支那車咁落後？<br />\n我冇直接答佢<b